  • Classes in solid5ive.cams.data.entities used by solid5ive.cams.data.entities 
    Class and Description
    Canteen
    Entity class for Canteen records.
    ContactType
    Represents three type of contact will be stored in database.
    MenuReference
    Entity class that records information of a menu item that is to be used for sales reporting.
    MenuTag
    Enumeration for various tag that stall owner can use to highlight their menu item.
    Orderline
    The entity class that records an entry of food order information in an order.
    Stall
    The entity class for the record of a stall in canteen, cacheable at runtime.
    User
    The entity class that records basic information about an user in the system.
    UserPermission
    User permission is not supposed to be managed by our system (It is managed by school/higher level department).
    UserRole
    User role is not supposed to be managed by our system (It is managed by school/higher level department).
